---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" noindex={true}>
  <div class="container legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 26, 2026</p>

    <h2>Data controller</h2>
    <p>FinanzasClara — Contact: vladys.z96@gmail.com</p>

    <h2>Data we collect</h2>
    <p>FinanzasClara collects data on a very limited basis:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Browsing data:</strong> Anonymous data via Google AdSense and analytics cookies (only if you accept cookies).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Purpose</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Anonymous traffic analysis to improve content.</li>
      <li>Show relevant ads (Google AdSense).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Legal basis</h2>
    <p>Data processing is based on your express consent (cookie acceptance).</p>

    <h2>Recipients</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google</strong> (Google Ireland Limited): advertising and analytics. Complies with the EU-US Data Privacy Framework.</li>
      <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> static files served by our hosting provider.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>You can exercise your rights of access, rectification, deletion, opposition and portability by contacting vladys.z96@gmail.com.</p>

    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p>Anonymous browsing data follows the policies of Google and our hosting provider.</p>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>We implement technical security measures (HTTPS, security headers) to protect information.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-page h1 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-page h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .legal-page p, .legal-page li { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
  .legal-page ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
</style>
